            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Scrape</strong> the bottom of the pan, then transfer the lot to a lightly oiled, oven-safe casserole dish</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cover</strong> tightly with foil and place in the oven for 30 min or until the chicken is cooked through</p>\r\n<p><strong>Reserve</strong> the pan for the next step</p>",
